claim.claim-text:
A surgical instrument comprising:
a handpiece;
a rod part at a distal end of the handpiece, the rod part including a surface for adhering a graft thereto;
a hollow pipe part configured to cover the rod part, the pipe part including an inner diameter with a predetermined clearance between the pipe part and the rod part;

and
a moving unit configured to move the pipe part relative to the rod part along an axial direction of the rod part.
